{"title":"三舍 B","photo":["$img/dorm/dorm3B.jpg","$img/dorm/dorm3b-2.jpg","$img/dorm/dorm3b-3.jpg","$img/dorm/dorm3b-4.jpg"],"id":"function/map/benbu/dorm/dorm3B","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"title","text":"三舍 B"},{"tag":"text","text":["住男生，共 14 层。入住外语学院英语系(包括公费师范生)、物理、文学、化学、地理、生科、数学、教育、马部、历史、心理学院学生。"]},{"tag":"title","text":"电梯"},{"tag":"text","text":["三舍 B 一共有三部电梯。其中，最左侧的是货梯，可以到达所有楼层；中间的为高层单层电梯，停 1、3、5、7、9、11、13 楼；最右侧的电梯为高层双层电梯，停 1、6、8、10、12、14 楼。"]},{"tag":"list","header":"寝室详细介绍","items":[{"text":"室内环境介绍","icon":"environment","path":"guide/dorm/detail/env"},{"text":"个人区域介绍","icon":"environment","path":"guide/dorm/detail/person"},{"text":"热水房","icon":"hot-water","path":"guide/dorm/detail/hot-water"},{"text":"洗漱间","icon":"washing-room","path":"guide/dorm/detail/washing"},{"text":"电梯","icon":"lift","path":"guide/dorm/detail/lift"},{"text":"自习室","icon":"study","path":"guide/dorm/detail/self-study"},{"text":"微波炉","icon":"study","path":"guide/dorm/detail/microwave"},{"text":"卫生间","icon":"toilet","path":"guide/dorm/detail/toilet"},{"text":"洗衣机","icon":"washer","path":"guide/dorm/detail/benbu-washer"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"寝室供电","items":[{"text":"供电时间","icon":"time","path":"guide/dorm/electricity/time"},{"text":"功率限制","icon":"power","path":"guide/dorm/electricity/power"},{"text":"缴纳电费","icon":"money","path":"guide/dorm/electricity/pay"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"寝室供网","items":[{"text":"寝室供网","icon":"network","path":"guide/dorm/network"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"规章制度","items":[{"text":"寝室门禁","icon":"door-guard","path":"guide/dorm/door-guard"},{"text":"走读与调宿","icon":"intro","path":"guide/dorm/day-reading"},{"text":"违禁物品","icon":"ban","path":"guide/dorm/ban"}]},{"tag":"list","items":[{"text":"Mr.Hope の建议","icon":"idea","path":"guide/dorm/advice"}]}],"time":"2020 年 9 月 1 日"}